cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.GR, cs.LG, cs.AI 

Reasoning: 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper deals with 3D reconstruction of dynamic scenes using object segmentation and pose estimation techniques. 
- cs.RO (Robotics) is also likely as the paper mentions the system's ability to handle large-scale environments and operate in an incremental manner, which are important considerations in robotics applications. 
- cs.GR (Graphics) is another possible category as the paper deals with generating 3D reconstructions of dynamic scenes. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is a possible category as the paper mentions the use of data-driven approaches for object pose estimation. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also a possible category as the paper deals with developing an end-to-end system for live reconstruction of dynamic environments, which involves various AI techniques such as object segmentation and pose estimation.
